        ("How extract facts for storage?", "LLM extraction prompt at session end: list durable user preferences/facts. Discard tool noise and ephemeral data."),
        ("Memory privacy?", "Strict user_id namespace. Encrypt at rest. Delete API for GDPR. Never cross-tenant retrieval."),
        ("Mem0 vs Zep vs roll-your-own?", "Mem0/Zep: managed memory layers. Roll-your-own pgvector if need full control and existing stack."),
        ("How handle contradictory memories?", "Store timestamp + source. On conflict, prefer newer or ask user. Consolidation job merges duplicates."),
