        ("Reflexion vs episodic?", "Reflexion: critique within same task retry. Episodic: store outcome for future different tasks."),
        ("Memory for multi-agent?", "Shared blackboard for task state; per-agent private scratchpad. Long-term memory at user level not agent level."),
        ("Eval memory quality?", "Recall: does agent remember stated preference 10 turns later? Precision: no hallucinated memories injected."),
        ("SDE3: memory architecture for support bot?", "Session buffer with rolling summary. Vector memory for account prefs. Episodic for resolved ticket patterns. TTL 90 days. GDPR purge API."),
